================================================================================
                           1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means the Smarting HOME Home Assistant integration, including all
custom components, blueprints, dashboards, translations, and documentation.

"License Key" means the unique alphanumeric key issued to the Licensee upon
purchase, required to activate PRO or ENTERPRISE features.

"Instance" means a single Home Assistant installation running on one (1)
physical or virtual host.

"DEMO Mode" means the limited functionality mode available without a valid
License Key, restricted to a maximum of 10 sensors and excluding AI features,
advanced automation blueprints, and premium dashboards.

