================================================================================
                      4. LICENSE VALIDATION
================================================================================

4.1 The Software requires periodic license validation via secure HTTPS
    connection to Smarting HOME servers (smartinghome.pl).

4.2 A grace period of seventy-two (72) hours is provided for temporary
    internet connectivity interruptions. During this period, the Software
    will continue to operate with full licensed functionality.

4.3 After the grace period expires without successful validation, the Software
    will revert to DEMO Mode until connectivity is restored.

4.4 License validation data transmitted includes only:
    - License Key (hashed)
    - Home Assistant instance identifier
    - Software version
    - Timestamp

    No personal data, energy usage data, or home network information is
    collected or transmitted.

================================================================================
                        5. LICENSE TIERS
================================================================================

  DEMO (Free)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  • Up to 10 computed sensors
  • Basic energy monitoring
  • No AI Energy Advisor
  • No automation blueprints
  • No premium dashboards
  • Community support only

  PRO (Paid Subscription)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  • Unlimited sensors (33+ computed, 3 binary, 5 switches, 2 selects, 3 numbers)
  • Full HEMS engine (G13 + RCE + SOC layers)
  • AI Energy Advisor (Google Gemini + Anthropic Claude)
  • All 7+ automation blueprints
  • All 3 premium dashboards
  • Night arbitrage, voltage cascade, PV surplus cascade
  • Email support
  • Single Instance

  ENTERPRISE (Paid Subscription)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  • All PRO features
  • Up to 5 Instances
  • Priority support (24h response SLA)
  • Custom blueprint development (upon request)
  • Early access to new features

================================================================================
                       6. SUBSCRIPTION & RENEWAL
================================================================================

6.1 PRO and ENTERPRISE licenses are subscription-based with monthly or annual
    billing cycles.

6.2 Upon subscription expiration, the Software will revert to DEMO Mode.
    No data is lost; full functionality is restored upon renewal.

6.3 Licensor reserves the right to adjust pricing for future subscription
    periods with thirty (30) days written notice.

