================================================================================
                      8. DATA & PRIVACY
================================================================================

8.1 The Software processes energy data locally within the Licensee's Home
    Assistant instance. No energy usage or personal data is transmitted to
    Smarting HOME servers.

8.2 If the Licensee enables the AI Energy Advisor feature, system state data
    is transmitted directly from the Licensee's instance to the chosen AI
    provider (Google or Anthropic) using the Licensee's own API key. Smarting
    HOME does not act as an intermediary for AI requests.

8.3 License validation data (Section 4.4) is processed in accordance with
    Polish data protection law and the EU General Data Protection Regulation
    (GDPR).

